-- Spain Towns Unable to Pay Wages on Time, Expansion Reports
-- B y   A n g e l i n e   B e n o i t
-- 2011-12-15T06:54:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-15/spain-towns-unable-to-pay-wages-on-time-expansion-reports.html
Several Spanish town authorities are
paying their public sector employees months late as they
struggle to face costs, and some of the nation’s 17 semi-
autonomous regions may soon face similar difficulties,  Expansion 
reported, citing workers’ unions.  To contact the reporter on this story:
